snippet.title: Brad Pitt Faces PRISON After Angelina Jolie Exposes Him
snippet.description:
Brad Pitt Faces PRISON After Angelina Jolie Exposes Him

Angelina Jolie and Brad Pitt’s custody battle just took an ugly turn after Angelina filed new court documents accusing her ex-husband of being physically aggressive towards her and her children.
The shocking revelation comes five years after Brad was cleared of similar allegations following an altercation with his son Maddox.
However, Angelina is now claiming she can offer proof of Brad’s dangerous behavior.
So what will happen to Brad if Angelina proves her accusations in court?
